    "description": "Test the 6 inventory API endpoints in order.\n\nPrerequisites:\n1. docker compose up --build\n2. Import Inventory-API.local.postman_environment.json\n3. Run requests top-to-bottom (later requests use IDs from earlier responses)\n\nSeeded demo data (ids after fresh seed):\n- provider_id: 1\n- storage_id: 1\n- client_id: 1\n- product_id: 1 (Earl Grey), 2 (Green Tea)",
